>   -DENABLE_DOCS=yes -DENABLE_NLS=OFF -DENABLE_TESTS=yes -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX="${env:LV_INSTALL_PREFIX}"

> -- Found OpenGL: opengl32

>   CMakeLists.txt:254 (FIND_PACKAGE)
windows.yml: Sort package names alphabetically
